title: Foster Poultry Farms, LLC Recalls Chicken Corn Dog and Ground Turkey on a Stick Products Due To Possible Extraneous Matter Contamination
summary: Editor’s Note: Details of this recall were updated on October 6, 2025, to reflect that there are ground turkey on a stick products included in the recalled products.
